3.0.0

* Changed web interface to Bootstrap 3
* Replaced hacky POST AJAX with dynamic pages rendered via Jade <http://jade-lang.com>
* Replaced AJAX login with HTTP-only cookies
* Refactored database code
* Refactored webserver code
* Updated username validation to allow accented letters (e.g. รก, รถ)

Planned:

* Support IPv6
* Better user playlist management
* Better channel settings interface
